data.title: Practical Modern JavaScript
data.subtitle: Dive into ES6 and the Future of JavaScript
data.author: Nicolás Bevacqua
data.description: To get the most out of modern JavaScript, you need learn the latest features of its parent specification, ECMAScript 6 (ES6). This book provides a highly practical look at ES6, without getting lost in the specification or its implementation details.
